data.description: Own your own slice of Tree lined Lower Mason Creek property, nestled in a park like 2.12 acres, this charming home overlooks beautiful Mason Creek and is loaded with catfish you can feed by the dam in your very own back yard while listening to the sound of the flowing water. Vaulted ceiling, tile throughout, Large Open floor plan great for entertaining, workshop, carport and so much more. This home is a must see to capture its true beauty and all it has to offer. There is an abundance of free roaming wildlife to enjoy while sitting outside on your private porch in this park like setting you can call home. This Home is a fisherman's dream come true!
